There was a prince named John.
He was cursed and bacame a frog.
His curse would only break if someone liked him with pure heart.
He met a girl named Jill who did not have a friend.
She always wanted to have a true friend.
She met this frog who wanted to stay with her and be her friend.
At first, Jill did not like the frog but after knowing that frog also needed a friend.
